## Mitigation / Best Practices

- Permissions: Always set execution rights with chmod +x.
- Validation: Use conditionals to verify user inputs securely.
- Comments: Document scripts for clarity and maintainability.
- Root usage: Switch to root only when necessary for system-wide tasks.
- Testing: Run scripts in controlled environments before applying to production.

